<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Join the Club - BikeRental</title>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.1/css/all.min.css">
    
    <style>
        /* ----------------------- 1. DESIGN SYSTEM ----------------------- */
        :root {
            --primary: #ff6b6b;
            --primary-dark: #ee5253;
            --secondary: #1e1e2f;
            --bg-body: #f4f7fe;
            --card-bg: #ffffff;
            --text-main: #2d3436;
            --text-muted: #636e72;
            --shadow: 0 15px 35px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }

        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif; }
        html, body { overflow-x: hidden; width: 100%; min-height: 100vh; }
        body { background: var(--bg-body); color: var(--text-main); display: flex; flex-direction: column; }

        /* ----------------------- 2. UNIVERSAL NAVBAR ----------------------- */
        .navbar {
            background: var(--secondary); padding: 12px 6%;
            display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;
            position: sticky; top: 0; z-index: 2000; box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
        }
        .navbar .brand { font-size: 1.8rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--primary); text-decoration: none; letter-spacing: 1px; }
        .navbar .brand span { color: #fff; font-weight: 300; }

        .nav-links { display: flex; gap: 10px; align-items: center; }
        .nav-links a {
            color: #fff; text-decoration: none; padding: 10px 18px; border-radius: 10px;
            font-weight: 500; font-size: 0.9rem; transition: 0.3s ease;
        }
        .nav-links a:hover { background: rgba(255, 107, 107, 0.1); color: var(--primary); }
        .nav-btn { background: var(--primary); color: #fff !important; }

        .menu-btn { display: none; cursor: pointer; color: #fff; font-size: 1.6rem; }

        /* Mobile Overlay Menu */
        .mobile-overlay {
            position: fixed; top: 0; right: -100%; width: 100%; height: 100%;
            background: var(--secondary); z-index: 2500; transition: 0.4s ease;
            display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; justify-content: center; gap: 25px;
        }
        .mobile-overlay.active { right: 0; }
        .mobile-overlay a { color: #fff; text-decoration: none; font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 600; }
        .close-menu { position: absolute; top: 25px; right: 25px; color: #fff; font-size: 2.2rem; cursor: pointer; }

        /* ----------------------- 3. SIGNUP BOX LAYOUT ----------------------- */
        main.container {
            flex: 1; display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center;
            padding: 50px 20px; animation: fadeInUp 0.8s ease;
        }

        @keyframes fadeInUp { from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); } to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); } }

        .form-card {
            background: var(--card-bg); width: 100%; max-width: 500px;
            padding: 45px 40px; border-radius: 30px; box-shadow: var(--shadow);
            text-align: center; border: 1px solid #edf2f7;
        }
        
        .form-card h2 { font-size: 2.2rem; font-weight: 800; color: var(--secondary); margin-bottom: 10px; }
        .form-card p.subtitle { color: var(--text-muted); font-size: 0.95rem; margin-bottom: 35px; }

        /* Form Group Styling */
        .input-group { position: relative; margin-bottom: 18px; text-align: left; }
        .input-group label { display: block; font-size: 0.8rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--secondary); margin-bottom: 8px; text-transform: uppercase; }
        .input-group i { position: absolute; left: 15px; top: 43px; color: #cbd5e0; font-size: 1.1rem; transition: 0.3s; z-index: 5; }
        
        .input-group input, .input-group select {
            width: 100%; padding: 14px 14px 14px 45px; border-radius: 12px;
            border: 2px solid #e2e8f0; font-size: 0.95rem; outline: none; transition: 0.3s;
            background: #fff; appearance: none;
        }
        .input-group input:focus, .input-group select:focus { border-color: var(--primary); box-shadow: 0 0 0 5px rgba(255, 107, 107, 0.1); }
        .input-group input:focus + i { color: var(--primary); }

        .btn-signup {
            width: 100%; padding: 16px; border-radius: 12px; border: none;
            background: var(--primary); color: #fff; font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 700;
            cursor: pointer; transition: 0.3s; margin-top: 15px; box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(255, 107, 107, 0.2);
        }
        .btn-signup:hover { background: var(--primary-dark); transform: translateY(-3px); }

        .alert-error {
            background: #fff5f5; color: #c53030; padding: 15px; border-radius: 15px;
            margin-bottom: 25px; font-size: 0.85rem; font-weight: 600; border: 1px solid #feb2b2;
            display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; justify-content: center;
        }

        .bottom-links { margin-top: 25px; font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--text-muted); }
        .bottom-links a { color: var(--primary); text-decoration: none; font-weight: 700; }
        .bottom-links a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }

        /* ----------------------- 4. UNIVERSAL FOOTER ----------------------- */
        footer { background: var(--secondary); color: #fff; padding: 70px 6% 30px; margin-top: auto; border-top: 6px solid var(--primary); }
        .footer-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(260px, 1fr)); gap: 40px; }
        
        .footer-brand h3 { color: var(--primary); font-size: 1.8rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 20px; }
        .footer-brand p { color: #b2bec3; font-size: 0.95rem; line-height: 1.7; }

        .footer-links h4 { color: #fff; margin-bottom: 20px; font-size: 1.1rem; position: relative; padding-bottom: 8px; }
        .footer-links h4::after { content:''; position: absolute; left: 0; bottom: 0; width: 30px; height: 2px; background: var(--primary); }
        .footer-links ul { list-style: none; }
        .footer-links a { color: #b2bec3; text-decoration: none; display: block; margin-bottom: 12px; font-size: 0.9rem; transition: 0.3s; }
        .footer-links a:hover { color: var(--primary); padding-left: 5px; }

        .footer-contact p { color: #b2bec3; font-size: 0.9rem; margin-bottom: 12px; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; }
        .footer-contact i { color: var(--primary); }

        .footer-form input, .footer-form textarea {
            width: 100%; padding: 12px; border-radius: 10px; border: none; background: #2d2d44; color: #fff; margin-bottom: 10px; outline: none;
        }
        .footer-form button { width: 100%; padding: 12px; background: var(--primary); color: #fff; border: none; border-radius: 10px; font-weight: 700; cursor: pointer; }

        .copyright { text-align: center; padding-top: 30px; margin-top: 50px; border-top: 1px solid #2d2d44; color: #636e72; font-size: 0.85rem; }

        /* ----------------------- 5. RESPONSIVE QUERIES ----------------------- */
        @media (max-width: 850px) {
            .nav-links { display: none; }
            .menu-btn { display: block; }
        }
        @media (max-width: 480px) {
            .form-card { padding: 35px 20px; border-radius: 25px; }
            .form-card h2 { font-size: 1.8rem; }
            .navbar { padding: 12px 5%; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <header class="navbar">
        <a href="/" class="brand">Bike<span>Rental</span></a>
        <div class="menu-btn" onclick="toggleMenu()"><i class="fas fa-bars"></i></div>
        <nav class="nav-links">
            <a href="/">Home</a>
            <a href="/login" class="nav-btn">Login Area</a>
        </nav>
    </header>

    <div class="mobile-overlay" id="mobileNav">
        <div class="close-menu" onclick="toggleMenu()"><i class="fas fa-times"></i></div>
        <a href="/" onclick="toggleMenu()">Home</a>
        <a href="/login" onclick="toggleMenu()">Login</a>
    </div>

    <main class="container">
        <div class="form-card">
            <h2>Sign Up</h2>
            <p class="subtitle">Quick and easy registration to start your first ride.</p>

            <% if (typeof message !== 'undefined' && message) { %>
                <div class="alert-error">
                    <i class="fas fa-circle-exclamation"></i> <%= message %>
                </div>
            <% } %>

            <form action="/signup" method="POST">
                <div class="input-group">
                    <label>Full Name</label>
                    <input type="text" name="name" placeholder="Aniket Gupta" required>
                    <i class="fas fa-user"></i>
                </div>

                <div class="input-group">
                    <label>Email Address</label>
                    <input type="email" name="email" placeholder="name@example.com" required>
                    <i class="fas fa-envelope"></i>
                </div>

                <div class="input-group">
                    <label>Phone Number</label>
                    <input type="tel" name="phone" placeholder="9876543210" required pattern="[0-9]{10}">
                    <i class="fas fa-phone"></i>
                </div>

                <div class="input-group">
                    <label>Choose Password</label>
                    <input type="password" name="password" placeholder="••••••••" required>
                    <i class="fas fa-lock"></i>
                </div>

                <div class="input-group">
                    <label>Account Type</label>
                    <select name="role" required>
                        <option value="user">Rider</option>
                    </select>
                    <i class="fas fa-motorcycle"></i>
                </div>

                <button type="submit" class="btn-signup">Create My Account</button>
            </form>

            <div class="bottom-links">
                <p>Already a rider? <a href="/login">Sign in here</a></p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>

    <footer>
        <div class="footer-grid">
            <div class="footer-brand">
                <h3>BikeRental</h3>
                <p>Providing premium urban mobility solutions since 2026. Safe, reliable, and performance-driven bikes for every journey.</p>
                <div style="display: flex; gap: 15px; margin-top: 25px;">
                    <a href="#" style="font-size: 1.2rem;"><i class="fab fa-facebook-f"></i></a>
                    <a href="#" style="font-size: 1.2rem;"><i class="fab fa-instagram"></i></a>
                    <a href="#" style="font-size: 1.2rem;"><i class="fab fa-x-twitter"></i></a>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="footer-links">
                <h4>Explore</h4>
                <ul>
                    <li><a href="/">Browse Fleet</a></li>
                    <li><a href="/login">Member Login</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#">Privacy Policy</a></li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="footer-links">
                <h4>Get in Touch</h4>
                <div class="footer-contact">
                    <p><i class="fas fa-envelope"></i> support@bikerental.com</p>
                    <p><i class="fas fa-phone"></i> +91 98765 43210</p>
                    <p><i class="fas fa-location-dot"></i> Hub Center, Civil Lines, MP</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="footer-form">
                <h4>Quick Feedback</h4>
                <form action="/feedback" method="POST">
                    <input type="text" placeholder="Your Name" required>
                    <textarea placeholder="Message..." rows="2" required></textarea>
                    <button type="submit">Submit</button>
                </form>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="copyright">
            <p>© <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> BikeRental System | Premium Mobility Solution | Developed by Aniket Kumar Gupta</p>
        </div>
    </footer>

    <script>
        function toggleMenu() {
            document.getElementById("mobileNav").classList.toggle("active");
        }
    </script>

</body>
</html>